Author: the_shame_train
Text: Waking up shaking and literally being able to feel your stomach folding in on itself and just thinking,  "it'll be okay once i have my black coffee"

Text: When I realized I was trying to justify doing 20-hour fasts while walking/running over six miles a day on the treadmill, and thinking that Gatorade Zero would just fix the dizziness...
